\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Yes, we had a cake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Any special decorations on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, just - you know, one tier cake in our day of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Did you have any sort of Naval insignia on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, we didn't actually, it was just a little - you know bits and pieces like the - confectioner's do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 What happened to the cake afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 I wouldn't know. There wasn't much left of it I suppose by the time my sister served it all out to the various, and - filled the bo
xes and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 You sent it to different people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Oh yes, because we had a lot of friends - presents from - one and another you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Were your presents on display at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Anybody make speeches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Oh well, just the norm
al you know. The vicar - the minister, he spoke and - my stepfather I suppose and George. Well like just the ordinary you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Was there any dancing and singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 How long did the whole thing go on for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Well we went away about - we were married at eleven in the morning and I think we - went away about half past one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Did you go on a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Yes, to Torquay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Did you have any practical jokes played on you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, not bad. No. No, I don't think we did. N
o, because we had to cross the ferry you see to get the train. 'Cos there were no coaches or cars in those days much as ever.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 How would you get down to the ferry then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Oh we - we had a car down to the ferry. And across to the station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Was it a car or a coach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 
Taxi thing. No, we didn't have - it wasn't a horse. It was a - it would be proper - you know, nothing - you know proper like a Cowley you know, old fashioned car. And actually - we were taken across the ferry on to the station, up to the station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 How long were you in Torquay for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Ten days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Did your husband carry you over the threshold?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, because we were - went to a hotel, I can remember that. I - I'm rather - you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 What about when you got back from honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Oh well no, we had a bit of laugh over that, but - we went back to my mother's you see. A - actually -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Why did you do that, not go straight to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Well, because they'd got as a meal when we got back you see in their home and t
hen we went to our own home after because - my sister had been and - she'd - got all the food in down at my place where I was going to live but - we went home for the evening meal and stayed for the evening you see. And that was that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 So you never actually got carried over the threshold?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, I never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Do you remember any other weddings when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Anything different from your own?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No, I didn't - I - I attended church weddings - in the church but I've never been - I don't think to a wedding - in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 The guests who came to the wedding, would it be mainly very close relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Yes, that was all, actually. There was - George and his father, and his sister and husband. And - three children
. And then there was my mother and father, stepfather, and my two sisters. And - the - the minister, that was - that came back - and then my mother's sister. But that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Did any of the family from your real father's side come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No. They 
didn't come because they - well there would only be my very elderly grandmother you see. She couldn't come. But they were quite happy about it all you know. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 When you had Colin and Jim, your sons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 What would they call your parents and your husband's parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 They called them grandma and grandpa. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16275245 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 Not granny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14811249 D  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 No. Oh no, they didn't have that. And George's father they used to call granda}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14945689\charrsid14952291 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7951666\charrsid14952291 , that was the thing - distinguish the two grandfather's you see.
\par }}